222
00:18:55,640 --> 00:19:02,240
it can be influenced by a whole bunch of different 
factors. So, if you think about for Thumbtack,  

223
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:07,280
it can be influenced by if there's a snowstorm 
out there, if the competition is bidding,  

224
00:19:07,280 --> 00:19:12,200
there's a whole bunch of exogenous factors that 
come into play. And the metric that I think is  

225
00:19:12,200 --> 00:19:19,080
slightly more actionable is a little harder to 
