example of Lyft. You have your liquidity is your  

228
00:19:30,280 --> 00:19:38,000
demand utilization, it's how many app opens turn 
into a ride, and what predicts this? What will  

229
00:19:38,000 --> 00:19:46,960
predict you and deciding to book a ride? For Lyft 
