231
00:19:53,120 --> 00:19:58,360
you were more than X person likely to convert and 
book a ride. If it's more than two minutes, if  

232
00:19:58,360 --> 00:20:03,120
it's five, then maybe you check at Uber, maybe you 
walk, maybe you take the bus. If it's two minutes,  

233
00:20:03,120 --> 00:20:06,560
it doesn't make a big enough difference, 
