239
00:20:31,400 --> 00:20:38,720
like this and limiting some of the effect of 
those exhaustive factors that I mentioned.

240
00:20:38,720 --> 00:20:44,800
Awesome. So, essentially watch fill rate 
is the term used that a lot of people love,  

