262
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:31,000
And so, to me, my answer would tend to be 
pretty classical, it would be like measure  

263
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:37,400
your product market fit the way you would 
for a normal company. So yeah, it's a bit  

264
00:22:37,400 --> 00:22:42,520
of an art more than the science, but I like the 
